# Ol Chiki IME (Input Method Editor)

Ol Chiki IME is a Windows desktop application that provides **phonetic keyboard mapping** for the **Ol Chiki script** (Santali language).  
It allows users to type Ol Chiki characters using standard Latin (QWERTY) keyboard input.

